    "description": "Keep your portions small with this char siu-inspired chicken. You'll pan fry chicken breast till golden, coat it in a rich five-spice sauce and serve up with cauliflower rice. Banging. Smaller portion providing 2 of your 5-a-day, a source of fibre and high in protein.",
